description: Saddle stitched binding, illustration of a figure on the ground, blowing bubbles, with an anthropomorphic guitar on a swing next to her. The swing's ropes comes from a group of flowers and plants above, which makes the backdrop for the title, printed in blue; 40 pp.
medium: Blue and black-and-white offset lithography; bound volume
title: Eye of the Majastic Creature, no. 3
